channel.title: Server Status page
channel.description:
Hey, sorry if I didn't post in the right section, but on my server status page my server continues to say offline, even thought it has been online for 4+ days straight, I thought maybe because I recently changed my IP address because I got a new router box and cable company, can anyone help me please?
